OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLow cloud retreating to eastern
OL,6,Fcoasts where it will persist for much
OL,7,Fof the day. Elsewhere its another fine
OL,8,Fand dry day with prolonged sunny
OL,9,Fperiods. Chance of an odd thundery
OL,10,Fshower in the southwest. Very warm or
OL,11,Fhot.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry with clear spells for
OL,14,Fmost, however low cloud near eastern
OL,15,Fcoasts will re-develop and extend into
OL,16,Fmany central areas by dawn. A warn
OL,17,Fnight in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
