OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FEarly cloud clearing, though
OL,6,Flingering near North Sea coasts.
OL,7,FOtherwise dry with long sunny spells.
OL,8,FA low chance of an isolated shower or
OL,9,Fthunderstorm in the far south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
